[This report provides reliable confirmation of the presumptive diagnosis with
which this thread was concluded in the previous post. Whether virus
infection was the actual cause of death of the farm worker is an open
question since the 2 patients under investigation reportedly displayed
similar symptoms irrespective of their Nipah virus status. - MOD.CP
